This page lists all of VRChat's [[wikipedia:April Fools' Day|April Fools' Day]] jokes.

==2022==
=== Joke Jam ===
On March 21, 2022, VRChat announced the [[Events#Joke Jam|Joke Jam]] world jam, which give creators a week to make a world using a jam-specific Bop System. This Bop System would track the total amount of "bops" users made, per world. This Bop System was an alpha test of Udon Analytics; an analytics system for creators. 

The theme of this jam was "jokes" and submissions coincidentally ended on April 1st. On the same day, a Joke Jam world row went live.
