File:Joke_Jam.png|Joke Jam logo
</gallery>

==2024==
=== Clock ===
{{Thumb|{{YouTube|wt6MOiLjFVY|thumb=File:YTThumb_wt6MOiLjFVY_CLASSIFIED.webp|title=2024-04-01 CLASSIFIED}}|2024 April Fools day video.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wt6MOiLjFVY 2024-04-01 CLASSIFIED] on ''YouTube''.</ref>}}
For April Fools 2024, VRChat released a video introducing new clock features on the [[Quick Menu#Clock|Quick Menu]]. This clock menu adds a bunch of non-standard and less than useful clocks and time formats.

=== VRRat Text Adventure ===
''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/VRRat#April_Fools'_2024_event|VRRat]] for more detailed information.''

Typing <code>We miss you VRRat</code> into your "personal notes" on your profile activates the text adventure. After completing, you temporary earn the "CHEESE" badge and a Cheese theme on the VRChat website. Note: The badge and theme are visual only and will not stay on your profile.

