===VRRat Community Takeover===
Many worlds were "taken over" by VRRat. Worlds included in VRRat's Community Takeover were selected as apart of a closed community intiative.<ref>[https://discord.com/channels/189511567539306508/189511567539306508/1356679058875875570 this was a part of a closed community intiative...] Flare on the VRChat ''Discord''.</ref> There were a total of 60 worlds with the <code>admin_vrrat_community_takeover</code> tag. The world row showcasing the worlds went live on April 1st at 2PM UTC
<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1906878174807703999 HMMM.............................. ||<t:1743516000:f>||] on ''X''.</ref>
<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1907072504398508106 🧀 It's FINALLY TIME AGAIN!!!!!!] on ''X''.</ref>
and ended on April 14th.
