=== VRC+ Quick Menu mascot swap ===
VRRat has replaced clickable VRCat with himself. Clicking VRRat multiple times will cause his own unique dialogue to appear. VRRat also has his own unique graphic for [[Earmuff Mode|earmuff mode]], and the back face of the Quick Menu.<gallery>
