==2026==
===Skip Leg Day===
In the [[Action Menu]], under Tools, a "Skip Leg Day" toggle was added. Enabling the toggle will remove the legs on all avatars present in the instance, including the local user. 

<gallery>
File:AprilFools2026 SkipLegDay AM.png|"Skip Leg Day" toggle in the Action Menu.
